http.title: Victoria Lodge offers serviced accommodation in Kenilworth
http.html:
This site uses cookies to enhance your experience. View our cookie policy to see which cookies we use and how to manage or remove them.

Dont show this message again
                 
     
       
         
           
 
       
     
           
     
 
Whether staying in Kenilworth on business or for pleasure, a warm welcome awaits you at Victoria Lodge. Our aim is to provide you with comfortable accommodation, a real home from home experience.

Victoria Lodge was previously a four-star Guest House and retains many of the features. It is now the first serviced accommodation in Kenilworth.

We are pleased to offer the following facilities:
Fully equipped kitchen
2 comfortable lounge / dining areas
Guest garden terrace
No smoking throughout the building
Private off-street parking
5 minute walk to town centre restaurants
BT Infinity Broadband
Separate laundry room
